Package: traffic-count
Architecture: any
Depends: libc6 (>= 2.17), libbpf-dev, clang (>= 12.0.0), llvm (>= 12.0.0), linux-libc-dev (>= 5.10)
Description: MAC-level traffic accounting service using eBPF TC
 traffic-count attaches eBPF programs to network interfaces to capture
 per-MAC ingress/egress byte and packet counters. Counters are
 periodically flushed to SQLite for persistence.
